對，你前面那支：

SELECT
v.CustomerNo,
v.HIGHRISK AS VERIFY_HIGHRISK,
b.HIGHRISK AS BSA_HIGHRISK
...

是在比對 所有共同存在於兩張表的 CustomerNo。

但你現在要驗證的是：

SELECT CustomerNo
FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
EXCEPT
SELECT CustomerNo
FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT a
JOIN CIF_Migrate_Mapping_TEMP b
    ON a.cif_key = b.NEW_CIF_KEY

這批「純台新戶」的 CustomerNo。

那應該改成：

WITH PURE_TS AS
(
    SELECT CustomerNo
    FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
    EXCEPT
    SELECT a.CustomerNo
    FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT a
    JOIN CIF_Migrate_Mapping_TEMP b
        ON a.cif_key = b.NEW_CIF_KEY
)
SELECT
    p.CustomerNo,
    v.HIGHRISK AS VERIFY_HIGHRISK,
    b.HIGHRISK AS BSA_HIGHRISK,
    CASE
        WHEN ISNULL(v.HIGHRISK,0) = ISNULL(b.HIGHRISK,0)
            THEN 'Same'
        ELSE 'Different'
    END AS CompareResult
FROM PURE_TS p
LEFT JOIN VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    ON p.CustomerNo = v.CustomerNo
LEFT JOIN BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT b
    ON p.CustomerNo = b.CustomerNo
ORDER BY p.CustomerNo;

⸻

如果你只想看有差異的：

WITH PURE_TS AS
(
    SELECT CustomerNo
    FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
    EXCEPT
    SELECT a.CustomerNo
    FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT a
    JOIN CIF_Migrate_Mapping_TEMP b
        ON a.cif_key = b.NEW_CIF_KEY
)
SELECT
    p.CustomerNo,
    v.HIGHRISK AS VERIFY_HIGHRISK,
    b.HIGHRISK AS BSA_HIGHRISK
FROM PURE_TS p
LEFT JOIN VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    ON p.CustomerNo = v.CustomerNo
LEFT JOIN BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT b
    ON p.CustomerNo = b.CustomerNo
WHERE ISNULL(v.HIGHRISK,0) <> ISNULL(b.HIGHRISK,0)
ORDER BY p.CustomerNo;

如果這支回傳 0 筆，表示：

✅ 純台新戶的 HIGHRISK 完全沒有變動。